{"tid":2302413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（腿張開）邱騰華：制定經貿策略需兩條腿走路","createTime":"2020-11-27T05:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T09:58:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4e27e80358b9358aaec76b69ec752629267cf9c4","tid":2302413,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2020/11/27/2645657_4464abc09394dcb0a42cfbc3a35e5d5f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2F2645657_4464abc09394dcb0a42cfbc3a35e5d5f.jpeg&h=c08bc11e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華表示，港府在制定經貿策略，要兩條腿走路，既關注管控疫情走出逆境，亦要盡量掌握商機。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華在出席記者會時稱，本港在防疫下，亦要抗逆境，找經濟出路，任何地方若有經濟復甦勢頭，本港都要盡量把握商機。<span class=\"red\">在重啟經濟找出路時，會配合國家內循環、融入國家發展</span>；開拓對本港發展有利的市場；以及支援受困行業，包括旅遊業和中小企等。<br />\n<br />\n關於旅遊業，他希望借助制定「躍動港島南」計劃和海洋公園的重生方案，為旅遊業及本地消閒注入新元素，其中海洋公園轉型方案預計明年初公布。政府認為，<span class=\"red\">珍寶海鮮舫擁有者無償送出海鮮舫予海洋公園，可與海洋公園重生計劃合拍</span>，並利用附近水體，增加海上設施，配合南區發展。<br />\n<br />\n展覽業發展方面，邱騰華指出，近期雖有大型展覽受疫情影響，但中長期會展業投放必須加強，當局已計劃開展灣仔北三棟政府大樓重建，發展為會展中心工作，而機管局亦會啟動亞博館第二期發展，合共增加約6.6萬平方呎樓面，展覽場地面積較現時多40%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2645657\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2645657&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=da164f7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2645657</a>"},{"pid":"121e57955c522461f704d81e7a72b1e6a9ebf6cd","tid":2302413,"uid":37596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:55:57.000Z","msg":"港共有幾ON9,海洋公園已經無錢,仲要養架爛船,將開支無限提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b5d5c5cb6c6afe541ed945044c478de898ee7b","tid":2302413,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:00:13.000Z","msg":"關稅華，行路不嬲都用對腳行，你用一隻腳行就仆街"},{"pid":"b2aed2a8b5248e41f0faa7d500cd9aeaf670808e","tid":2302413,"uid":3161,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"佢用開四隻腳行"},{"pid":"9db70f428cb75e8aa9921cdf2e2d352c8fca3c8f","tid":2302413,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2aed2a8b5248e41f0faa7d500cd9aeaf670808e","tid":2302413,"uid":3161,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"佢用開四隻腳行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde0973cfa5d0a7baa30c7f652a413fcc9225236","tid":2302413,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:08:20.000Z","msg":"又學埋D共式中文<br />\n成篇野完全冇重點"},{"pid":"72c7278ee9d298b35c4be75f1968107408440dea","tid":2302413,"uid":66957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2aed2a8b5248e41f0faa7d500cd9aeaf670808e","tid":2302413,"uid":3161,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"佢用開四隻腳行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbea9c47cf1df9b3f00ff53e2eaee02649e19e36","tid":2302413,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:09:16.000Z","msg":"邱騰華搞港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809b406633089b5fb9d10c7f0d0fd945a946ec12","tid":2302413,"uid":64692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:59:49.000Z","msg":"共產中文"},{"pid":"6b21c99721f13463a6c5014850f7c5e1fb34e513","tid":23024